00:01:01.094 --> 00:01:03.665 position:35% line:89% align:start
Um. Or not?

00:01:04.766 --> 00:01:05.967 position:41% line:89% align:start
Senpai?

00:01:06.099 --> 00:01:08.268 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

