00:01:11.104 --> 00:01:13.273 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Sure, anything.

00:01:14.509 --> 00:01:17.579 position:10% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Which do you prefer?
Bears or bunny rabbits?

00:01:18.913 --> 00:01:20.380 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
What?

00:01:20.515 --> 00:01:23.383 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, which one is it then?
This is very important.

00:01:23.518 --> 00:01:24.786 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh.

00:01:24.919 --> 00:01:26.854 position:21% line:89% align:start
So, bears or bunnies?

00:01:26.988 --> 00:01:29.389 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] You have to pick one.
So which is it?

00:01:29.524 --> 00:01:32.326 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, if I had to choose
I'd go with bears.

00:01:32.459 --> 00:01:35.295 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
Understood. Here you go!

00:01:36.129 --> 00:01:38.165 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's this for?

00:01:38.298 --> 00:01:41.002 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's a tasty pick-me-up.
Cute, right?

00:01:41.134 --> 00:01:44.072 position:13% line:83% align:start
People get kind of run down
around this time of day.

00:01:44.204 --> 00:01:46.306 position:27% line:83% align:start
And somebody from
general affairs

00:01:46.440 --> 00:01:47.942 position:27% line:89% align:start
gave these to us.

00:01:48.076 --> 00:01:51.211 position:16% line:83% align:start
I was planning on passing
them out to everyone else later,

00:01:51.345 --> 00:01:52.747 position:24% line:89% align:start
but then I saw you

00:01:52.880 --> 00:01:55.115 position:10% line:83% align:start
and I thought you might like
to have yours early.

00:01:56.751 --> 00:01:59.386 position:13% line:83% align:start
It'll be our little secret,
okay?

00:02:01.723 --> 00:02:04.391 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] One of my superiors
at work, my Senpai,

00:02:04.525 --> 00:02:06.493 position:21% line:89% align:start
is so small and cute!

00:03:39.219 --> 00:03:42.590 position:19% line:77% align:start
Who's ready for another
wonderful workday? Oh.

00:03:44.859 --> 00:03:47.628 position:19% line:83% align:start
Guess it'll just be me
until everyone else gets in.

00:03:52.365 --> 00:03:54.202 position:35% line:89% align:start
Come here.

00:03:54.334 --> 00:03:55.536 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:03:56.037 --> 00:03:57.538 position:16% line:89% align:start
I guess I got here early.

00:03:59.173 --> 00:04:00.307 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:01.408 --> 00:04:02.944 position:33% line:89% align:start
