out on her desk like that.

00:04:05.213 --> 00:04:06.413 position:35% line:89% align:start
[both sigh]

00:04:06.547 --> 00:04:09.349 position:5% line:89% align:start
Um. Good to see you, Shinozaki.

00:04:09.951 --> 00:04:12.954 position:5% line:83% align:start
-Senpai, is that you down there?
-It is.

00:04:13.087 --> 00:04:14.622 position:24% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?

00:04:14.756 --> 00:04:18.793 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh, just grabbing this.
My pen rolled under here.

00:04:18.926 --> 00:04:20.895 position:30% line:83% align:start
Oh, well then,
I'll get out of your way!

00:04:21.028 --> 00:04:23.698 position:13% line:83% align:start
-That would be appreciated.
-[thuds]

00:04:23.831 --> 00:04:25.099 position:41% line:89% align:start
Senpai.

00:04:25.233 --> 00:04:29.804 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:04:29.937 --> 00:04:31.606 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

