You bumped your head,
and I went to help--

00:04:40.081 --> 00:04:41.348 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hold on, you're freaking me out!

00:04:41.481 --> 00:04:43.684 position:7% line:83% align:start
You don't have to panic, okay?
It's fine.

00:04:44.585 --> 00:04:45.920 position:35% line:89% align:start
[both sigh]

00:04:46.053 --> 00:04:48.321 position:44% line:89% align:start
