something down there.

00:04:56.264 --> 00:04:58.331 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, not you too!

00:04:58.465 --> 00:05:01.035 position:13% line:83% align:start
I think that dirty thoughts
are very bad.

00:05:01.169 --> 00:05:05.606 position:7% line:83% align:start
