it was nothing like that!

00:05:08.776 --> 00:05:09.610 position:38% line:89% align:start
[clicks]

00:05:09.744 --> 00:05:11.245 position:33% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Hey, Senpai.

00:05:11.378 --> 00:05:13.281 position:10% line:83% align:start
Did you get a chance to look
over the documents I sent?

00:05:13.413 --> 00:05:14.414 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:05:14.549 --> 00:05:15.415 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
Thanks for reminding me.

00:05:15.550 --> 00:05:17.552 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll look over them now.

00:05:21.522 --> 00:05:22.657 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, my gosh!

00:05:22.790 --> 00:05:23.691 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:05:23.825 --> 00:05:25.293 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is there something
wrong with them?

00:05:25.425 --> 00:05:27.695 position:10% line:89% align:start
There's something, all right.

00:05:30.430 --> 00:05:33.000 position:5% line:83% align:start
These were all done really well,
great job!

00:05:34.434 --> 00:05:35.770 position:27% line:89% align:start
Who's a good boy!

00:05:35.903 --> 00:05:38.405 position:30% line:83% align:start
Um, thank you.
I worked really hard on them.

00:05:38.539 --> 00:05:41.008 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're the bestest boy,
yes, you are.

00:05:41.142 --> 00:05:42.643 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Senpai.

00:05:42.777 --> 00:05:46.013 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] Those two seem to
get along really well. I wonder.

00:05:46.147 --> 00:05:47.982 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is their dynamic normal

00:05:48.115 --> 00:05:50.450 position:21% line:83% align:start
for an ordinary pair
of coworkers?

00:05:50.585 --> 00:05:52.854 position:5% line:89% align:start
Certainly doesn't feel ordinary.

00:05:52.987 --> 00:05:55.790 position:16% line:83% align:start
They're more like the two
leads in a rom-com.

00:05:55.923 --> 00:05:57.490 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:06:00.393 --> 00:06:02.096 position:27% line:83% align:start
You want me to go
scout a location?

00:06:02.230 --> 00:06:05.432 position:7% line:83% align:start
Yeah. We have a drinking party
happening soon.

00:06:05.566 --> 00:06:07.467 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'd do it,
but something came up.

00:06:07.602 --> 00:06:10.137 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ah. Sure, I can help out.

00:06:10.271 --> 00:06:12.506 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's great. You know what?

00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:14.642 position:21% line:83% align:start
The more perspectives
the better, I say.

00:06:14.775 --> 00:06:17.410 position:19% line:83% align:start
Katase, would you like
to join Shinozaki?

00:06:17.545 --> 00:06:20.915 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yes! I'm so happy you asked me.

00:06:21.048 --> 00:06:23.317 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:06:23.450 --> 00:06:25.686 position:24% line:83% align:start
I wonder what kind
of place it is.

00:06:25.820 --> 00:06:28.623 position:30% line:83% align:start
Whatever it is,
I just hope the food is tasty!

00:06:30.358 --> 00:06:32.693 position:13% line:83% align:start
Apparently, the restaurant
is on the top floor.

00:06:32.827 --> 00:06:34.394 position:13% line:89% align:start
I hope we're near a window.

00:06:34.528 --> 00:06:37.598 position:7% line:83% align:start
