bet it's gonna be pretty trendy.

00:06:37.732 --> 00:06:39.000 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
That's a good point, Shinozaki!

00:06:39.133 --> 00:06:40.400 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:06:41.035 --> 00:06:43.838 position:24% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] Perfection!
It's all coming together.

00:06:43.971 --> 00:06:46.941 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now all they need to do
is keep the mood going.

00:06:47.074 --> 00:06:51.145 position:38% line:83% align:start
Oh, dear.
I am just, oh, so tipsy.

00:06:51.279 --> 00:06:53.147 position:19% line:89% align:start
What? That's not good.

00:06:53.281 --> 00:06:56.250 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:06:56.384 --> 00:06:58.786 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'll have to take you home
with me.

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:01.255 position:5% line:89% align:start
I would love it if you did that.

00:07:01.389 --> 00:07:04.592 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:07:04.725 --> 00:07:09.664 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Shinozaki, will you?
-Of course, always.

00:07:12.133 --> 00:07:13.167 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:07:13.301 --> 00:07:14.869 position:13% line:83% align:start
I could've gotten a ticket
for how fast

00:07:15.002 --> 00:07:17.104 position:10% line:89% align:start
that was going to spicy town.

00:07:17.772 --> 00:07:19.307 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[HAYAKAWA] Manager?
-Hmm?

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.574 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hayakawa?

00:07:20.708 --> 00:07:22.276 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's me.

00:07:22.410 --> 00:07:24.211 position:5% line:83% align:start
I thought you mentioned that you
had something come up tonight,

00:07:24.345 --> 00:07:25.813 position:35% line:89% align:start
didn't you?

00:07:30.151 --> 00:07:32.420 position:21% line:83% align:start
-I see. That tracks.
-[grunts].

00:07:32.553 --> 00:07:34.487 position:35% line:83% align:start
Aren't you
the least bit curious?

00:07:34.622 --> 00:07:36.223 position:19% line:83% align:start
You've known Shinozaki
for a while.

00:07:36.357 --> 00:07:38.526 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wait. Of course!

00:07:39.492 --> 00:07:41.662 position:19% line:89% align:start
How thoughtless of me!

00:07:42.964 --> 00:07:44.365 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
If you ever need anything,

00:07:44.497 --> 00:07:46.499 position:27% line:83% align:start
feel free to come
and ask me, okay?

00:07:46.634 --> 00:07:48.002 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
Should I root for Age Gap,

00:07:48.135 --> 00:07:49.870 position:21% line:83% align:start
Coworkers to Lovers,
Fluff with a Happy Ending?

00:07:50.004 --> 00:07:52.006 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] Stop looking at me
like that, you big dummy.

00:07:52.139 --> 00:07:54.608 position:13% line:83% align:start
