00:07:57.945 --> 00:08:00.247 position:30% line:83% align:start
I must choose.
But they're both so beautiful.

00:08:00.381 --> 00:08:01.882 position:7% line:89% align:start
How about you just don't then?

00:08:02.016 --> 00:08:04.685 position:10% line:83% align:start
Now, keep me out of whatever
weirdness is in your head.

00:08:04.819 --> 00:08:06.620 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, you sure?

00:08:06.754 --> 00:08:07.922 position:24% line:89% align:start
Aggressively sure.

00:08:08.055 --> 00:08:10.024 position:19% line:83% align:start
There is nothing there,
trust me.

00:08:10.157 --> 00:08:11.225 position:38% line:89% align:start
