00:08:14.295 --> 00:08:16.664 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm not sure I like
how disappointed you are.

00:08:16.797 --> 00:08:19.266 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, be that as it may.

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:21.736 position:13% line:83% align:start
Since you're already here,
you might as well come

00:08:21.869 --> 00:08:23.337 position:10% line:83% align:start
-and watch the show with me.
-What?

00:08:23.938 --> 00:08:28.175 position:10% line:83% align:start
Thank you for dining with us.
Your table is ready now.

00:08:28.309 --> 00:08:29.977 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please, follow me.

00:08:30.811 --> 00:08:32.646 position:19% line:89% align:start
Quickly, to our seats!

00:08:32.780 --> 00:08:35.016 position:5% line:89% align:start
How would I get roped into this?

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:40.121 position:35% line:83% align:start
[WAITRESS]
And here we are.

00:08:40.254 --> 00:08:41.922 position:16% line:83% align:start
These are special tables
that allow you

00:08:42.056 --> 00:08:43.958 position:13% line:89% align:start
to fully take in the view.

00:08:44.091 --> 00:08:47.461 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'll let you settle in and then
I'll be back for your order.

00:08:47.595 --> 00:08:48.963 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:08:49.096 --> 00:08:50.931 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] The stage is set,
the stars are seated

00:08:51.065 --> 00:08:52.967 position:27% line:83% align:start
