[AKINA]
Stop thinking about food!

00:09:04.812 --> 00:09:06.747 position:10% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I've never eaten
anywhere like this.

00:09:06.881 --> 00:09:08.349 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
It's a first for me too.

00:09:08.482 --> 00:09:10.785 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I'd expect nothing
less from our manager.

00:09:10.918 --> 00:09:12.253 position:21% line:89% align:start
He's got great taste.

00:09:12.386 --> 00:09:14.121 position:30% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] I hate
how far off script they are,

00:09:14.255 --> 00:09:16.290 position:7% line:83% align:start
but they seem to be having fun,
so I guess it's all right?

00:09:16.424 --> 00:09:18.659 position:24% line:83% align:start
You sure seem to be
enjoying yourself.

00:09:18.793 --> 00:09:20.194 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
I'm having a ball!

00:09:20.327 --> 00:09:21.162 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:09:21.295 --> 00:09:22.196 position:38% line:89% align:start
You see.

00:09:22.329 --> 00:09:23.798 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:24.465 --> 00:09:25.900 position:30% line:89% align:start
The thing is...

00:09:26.033 --> 00:09:27.134 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:09:27.835 --> 00:09:29.937 position:21% line:83% align:start
