00:09:45.352 --> 00:09:46.454 position:30% line:89% align:start
Do you see it?

00:09:46.587 --> 00:09:48.589 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
What am I looking for?

00:09:48.722 --> 00:09:49.890 position:10% line:89% align:start
If you look right over there

00:09:50.024 --> 00:09:51.358 position:27% line:83% align:start
you can pick out
our office building.

00:09:51.492 --> 00:09:54.462 position:30% line:83% align:start
I don't see it.
Hang on, let me adjust.

00:09:54.595 --> 00:09:57.031 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both grunt]

00:09:57.164 --> 00:09:59.266 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Shiori humming]

00:09:59.400 --> 00:10:00.668 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

